servation</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A curse mechanic tied to how you use mirrors</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hidden rooms, secrets, and fragments of your past</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The satisfaction of actually finishing a game in one sitting</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3318950/extras/1e9f612fca87cbd94d9d202c4c8c0edd.avif?t=1755808933\" width=600 height=256 /></span></p>",
